# Summary
This documentation explains how to use permission groups in Amplitude Enterprise to efficiently manage user permissions at scale by assigning multiple users to groups with specific project access levels, rather than configuring permissions individually, with detailed instructions for creating and managing groups and examples of how permission inheritance works.

